                        <p class="card-text">Every day you'll have the opportunity to improve someone's quality of life and bring comfort to families in need.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                        <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3">
                            <img src="~/images/Careers/training-development.png" alt="Training & Development" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; object-fit: contain;">
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Training & Development</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">We provide comprehensive training programs and ongoing professional development opportunities to help you grow in your career.</p>
